@startuml
    title Strategy - seleccion por factory
    left to right direction
    skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
    skinparam shadowing false
    skinparam roundcorner 8
    skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
    skinparam class {
      BackgroundColor #F8FAFC
      BorderColor #334155
      ArrowColor #334155
      FontColor #0F172A
    }
    hide empty members

    package "main" #EEF2FF {
      class Main <<cliente>>
    }

    package "pattern" #ECFDF5 {
      class PriceCalculator <<Context>>
      interface PricingStrategy <<Strategy>>
      class StandardPricing
      class VipPricing
  class PricingStrategyFactory <<seleccion>>
    }

    PricingStrategy <|.. StandardPricing
    PricingStrategy <|.. VipPricing
    PriceCalculator --> PricingStrategy : delega algoritmo
    Main ..> PriceCalculator : usa contexto
    PricingStrategyFactory ..> PricingStrategy : retorna
Main ..> PricingStrategyFactory : solicita estrategia

    note bottom of PriceCalculator
    La seleccion queda fuera del contexto; el contexto solo delega.
    end note
    @enduml
